OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1781384335
OL,3,CMel Tottoh urges fans to not ignore
OL,4,Cblood cancer warning signs
OL,6,FMel Tottoh, who played for Preston
OL,7,FNorth End was told for more than a
OL,8,Fyear that his agonising back and rib
OL,9,Fpain was likely caused by ageing, a
OL,10,Fpulled muscle, or a cracked rib before
OL,11,Fhe was diagnosed with myeloma in 2021.
OL,13,FBy the time doctors discovered the
OL,14,Fcause, the blood cancer had already
OL,15,Fcaused significant damage, eating
OL,16,Fholes in the father-of-three's ribs,
OL,17,Fspine and skull.
OL,19,FMel, from Freckleton, in Lancashire,
OL,20,Fsaid the first signs appeared before
OL,21,Fthe Covid-19 pandemic.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1781384335
OL,3,CMel Tottoh urges fans to not ignore
OL,4,Cblood cancer warning signs
OL,6,F"It started pre-Covid. A few pains and
OL,7,Faches, which was quite normal. I was
OL,8,Fan active sportsman, playing a bit of
OL,9,Fkarate and playing a lot of golf," he
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FAt the end of 2019, Mel and his wife
OL,13,FMelanie regularly walked between six
OL,14,Fand 10 miles a day, several times a
OL,15,Fweek.
OL,17,F"We loved it," he said. "But then I
OL,18,Fstarted feeling really fatigued. I
OL,19,Fcould still do it, but I would be
OL,20,Ftotally wiped out and that was very
OL,21,Funusual for me.
OL,26,@qD@bO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1781384335
OL,3,CMel Tottoh urges fans to not ignore
OL,4,Cblood cancer warning signs
OL,6,F"I phoned the doctors and they said it
OL,7,Fwas a function of getting older."
OL,9,FAs the months went on, Mel began
OL,10,Fexperiencing pain in his ribs while
OL,11,Fplaying golf. Afterwards, he would
OL,12,Fsuffer pain in his spine and struggle
OL,13,Fto turn his neck.
OL,15,FDoctors initially believed he had
OL,16,Fpulled a muscle, But the symptoms
OL,17,Fcontinued to worsen.
OL,19,FOne day while playing golf, Mel felt a
OL,20,Fsudden, intense pain in his ribs
OL,21,Fduring a swing.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1781384335
OL,3,CMel Tottoh urges fans to not ignore
OL,4,Cblood cancer warning signs
OL,6,F"It felt like I'd smashed my ribs," he
OL,7,Fsaid.
OL,9,FFrom that moment, what had started as
OL,10,Faches and pains became "excruciating".
OL,12,FWhat are the signs of myeloma?
OL,14,FDoctors later suspected a cracked rib
OL,15,Fand prescribed increasingly strong
OL,16,Fpainkillers, but the pain persisted.
OL,18,FX-rays, CT scans and MRI scans failed
OL,19,Fto reveal the cause.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@cO]rD@XOUrD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1781384335
OL,3,CMel Tottoh urges fans to not ignore
OL,4,Cblood cancer warning signs
OL,6,F"Because of all these symptoms, I
OL,7,Fthought it can't just be my body
OL,8,Fageing in literally four months," Mel
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"I was sleeping on the settee because
OL,12,FI couldn't get up the stairs."
OL,14,FThe breakthrough finally came after a
OL,15,Fcomprehensive blood test revealed an M-
OL,16,Fprotein, a key indicator of myeloma.
OL,18,FMel received the diagnosis during a
OL,19,Fphone call from his GP surgery.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@aO]sD@AOUtD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1781384335
OL,3,CMel Tottoh urges fans to not ignore
OL,4,Cblood cancer warning signs
OL,6,F"I got a call saying my potassium
OL,7,Flevels were off, so I went in and a
OL,8,Flocum said, 'As you know, you've got
OL,9,Fmultiple myeloma.'
OL,11,F"And I said, 'Sorry, I don't know
OL,12,Fanything about that.'
OL,14,F"I hadn't heard of it before, and he
OL,15,Fsaid it's an incurable blood cancer.
OL,17,F"I swear, from that moment on, for the
OL,18,Fnext four or five minutes, I couldn't
OL,19,Fhear a word he said. I was completely
OL,20,Ffloored by it.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1781384335
OL,3,CMel Tottoh urges fans to not ignore
OL,4,Cblood cancer warning signs
OL,6,F"I was really anxious because my
OL,7,Ffather had died of cancer and, in
OL,8,Frecent years, I had lost two brothers
OL,9,Fto cancer as well. All I heard was the
OL,10,Fword cancer and thought my life was
OL,11,Fgoing to be over.
OL,13,F"So when they gave me the news, I
OL,14,Fthought this was it."
OL,16,FMel first shared the diagnosis with
OL,17,Fhis wife before speaking to their
OL,18,Fchildren.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUvD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1781384335
OL,3,CMel Tottoh urges fans to not ignore
OL,4,Cblood cancer warning signs
OL,6,F"Even though I was trying to be
OL,7,Fpositive and upbeat about it all, the
OL,8,Fthought was: how do I make everything
OL,9,Fright for Melanie and the children?"
OL,11,FFollowing his diagnosis, Mel underwent
OL,12,Fa stem cell transplant in 2021 and
OL,13,Fresponded exceptionally well to
OL,14,Ftreatment, entering remission quickly.
OL,16,FNow, Mel is sharing his story as part
OL,17,Fof Myeloma Awareness Week, 15 - 21
OL,18,FJune, joining Myeloma UK's Know the
OL,19,FWarning Signs campaign in a bid to
OL,20,Fhelp others recognise the symptoms
OL,21,Fsooner.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1781384335
OL,3,CMel Tottoh urges fans to not ignore
OL,4,Cblood cancer warning signs
OL,6,FHis warning comes as Myeloma UK
OL,7,Festimates that around 670 people
OL,8,Facross the UK will be diagnosed with
OL,9,Fmyeloma during the course of this
OL,10,Fsummer's World Cup tournament alone.
OL,12,FAlthough his recovery has been slow
OL,13,Fand he still experiences fatigue and
OL,14,Foccasional spinal pain, radiotherapy
OL,15,Fhas significantly improved his
OL,16,Fsymptoms.
OL,18,FThe cancer remains incurable and is
OL,19,Fexpected to return at some stage,
OL,20,Falthough doctors cannot predict when.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1781384335
OL,3,CMel Tottoh urges fans to not ignore
OL,4,Cblood cancer warning signs
OL,6,FAs part of Myeloma UK's latest
OL,7,Fawareness campaign, Mel is featured
OL,8,Fwith yellow warning signs painted
OL,9,Fdirectly onto the areas of his body
OL,10,Fwhere his symptoms first appeared,
OL,11,Fencouraging others to seek medical
OL,12,Fadvice if something does not feel
OL,13,Fright.
OL,15,FWith football fans preparing to follow
OL,16,Fevery moment of this summer's World
OL,17,FCup, Mel hopes his story will
OL,18,Fencourage people not to ignore
OL,19,Fpersistent symptoms.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1781384335
OL,3,CMel Tottoh urges fans to not ignore
OL,4,Cblood cancer warning signs
OL,6,F"If you have a combination of
OL,7,Fpersistent symptoms, including pains
OL,8,Fin the hands and feet and feeling cold
OL,9,Fall the time, do not ignore them," he
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"Don't be brushed off - you know your
OL,13,Fbody. If in doubt, check it out."
OL,15,FClick here to join the UK's stem cell
OL,16,Fdonor register.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@bO]tD@AOUuD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
